utilities.eval

Class CorpusDepot

  • java.lang.Object
    • utilities.eval.CorpusDepot

  • public class CorpusDepot
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used in Evaluation to evaluate a LanguageModel parallelized with a corpus. Lines ready for evaluation are then stored with this class in a stack by a CorpusReader, ready to be picked up by a CorpusEvaluator.
    Author:
    Dennis Ulmer
